trans-unit.source: Represents a method that handles the <xref href="System.AppDomain.TypeResolve"></xref>, <xref href="System.AppDomain.ResourceResolve"></xref>, or <xref href="System.AppDomain.AssemblyResolve"></xref> event of an <xref href="System.AppDomain"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en metode som behandler den <xref href="System.AppDomain.TypeResolve"> </xref>, <xref href="System.AppDomain.ResourceResolve"> </xref>, eller <xref href="System.AppDomain.AssemblyResolve"> </xref> hendelse for en <xref href="System.AppDomain"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: If the runtime class loader cannot resolve a reference to an assembly, type, or resource, the corresponding events are raised to give the callback a chance to tell the runtime which assembly the referenced assembly, type, or resource is in.
trans-unit.target: Hvis klassen kjøretidslasteren ikke kan løse en referanse til en samling, type eller ressurs, er de tilsvarende hendelsene oppstå hvis du vil gi tilbakeringing mulighet til å be kjøretiden hvilken samling henviste samlingen, type eller ressurs.

trans-unit.source: It is the responsibility of the ResolveEventHandler to return the assembly that resolves the type, assembly, or resource, or to return null if the assembly is not recognized.
trans-unit.target: Det er ansvarlig for ResolveEventHandler til å returnere samlingen som løser type, samlingen eller ressurs, eller til å returnere null hvis samlingen ikke gjenkjennes.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Resolving Assembly Loads](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and the <xref:System.AppDomain.ResourceResolve?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.AppDomain.AssemblyResolve?displayProperty=fullName>, and <xref:System.AppDomain.ReflectionOnlyAssemblyResolve?displayProperty=fullName> events.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [løsning samlingen laster](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og <xref:System.AppDomain.ResourceResolve?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.AppDomain.AssemblyResolve?displayProperty=fullName>, og <xref:System.AppDomain.ReflectionOnlyAssemblyResolve?displayProperty=fullName>hendelser.</xref:System.AppDomain.ReflectionOnlyAssemblyResolve?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.AppDomain.AssemblyResolve?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.AppDomain.ResourceResolve?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > Beginning with the [!INCLUDE[net_v40_long](~/add/includes/net-v40-long-md.md)], the ResolveEventHandler event is raised for all assemblies, including resource assemblies.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT] > Begynner med den [!INCLUDE[net_v40_long](~/add/includes/net-v40-long-md.md)], ResolveEventHandler-hendelsen starter for alle samlinger, inkludert ressursen samlinger.

trans-unit.source: In earlier versions, the event was not raised for resource assemblies.
trans-unit.target: Hendelsen ble ikke startet for ressursen samlinger i tidligere versjoner.

trans-unit.source: If the operating system is localized, the handler might be called multiple times: once for each culture in the fallback chain.
trans-unit.target: Hvis operativsystemet lokalisert, behandlingsprogrammet kan kalles flere ganger: én gang for hver kulturen i fallback kjeden.

trans-unit.source: Every derived class of <xref:System.Delegate> and <xref:System.MulticastDelegate> has a constructor and an `Invoke` method.
trans-unit.target: Hver avledet type <xref:System.Delegate>og <xref:System.MulticastDelegate>har en konstruktør og en `Invoke` metode.</xref:System.MulticastDelegate> </xref:System.Delegate>

trans-unit.source: See the C++ code example in the description for the <xref:System.Delegate> class.
trans-unit.target: Se C++ kodeeksempel i beskrivelsen for <xref:System.Delegate>klasse.</xref:System.Delegate>
